# Eye of Zeus scope allowlist.
# Copy this to scope.txt (same directory) or pass it with --scope FILE.
# One entry per line. Anything the tool attacks must match an entry here,
# otherwise it is refused. Blank lines and # comments are ignored.
#
# Supported entry types:
#   - single IPv4        e.g. 192.168.56.10
#   - CIDR range         e.g. 192.168.56.0/24
#   - BSSID (AP MAC)     e.g. AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF   (case-insensitive)

192.168.56.0/24
10.0.0.0/24
AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF
